Brainstorming action space / tools for LLM to 
generate airfoil designs and make modifications.

Considerations:
    -Because LLMs generate text via probabilistic token prediction,explicit high-precision decimal ouputs are limited + biased by training data  and model priors.
    -Solution: LLM generates lower and upper bounds -> sample for higher precison decimal value for direct value modifcations / otherwise uses a computaional method. 

LLM actions (in progress):
1) Generate new design: 
    Methods:
        -Gaussian sampling from priors (similar to LLM PSO) (LLM chooses the next variant)
        -LLM generated (new value for each paramter)
2) Modify existing design <- modifies specific paramters from existing design based on inspiration samples
3) Design-by-Morphing (DbM) approach (promising ASO action for RL agents (combines multiple designs -> new airfoil))
    (i.e https://doi.org/10.1093/jcde/qwaf124, https://doi.org/10.1093/jcde/qwad059) 
4) ... work in progress 